<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/311092-what-could-be-so-especial-about-it-seems">What could be so especial about it, seems like any other Holloywood-type sci-fiction story, like the transformers!!???</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_311092'><a id="like_count_community_question_311092" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/311092?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">10 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17182126-steelheart">like</a></span>

