<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/215132-was-i-the-only-one-who-thought-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Was I the only one who thought the weakness would be that the bullet had blood on it, after going through the robber? The "must not be afraid" seemed like a bit of a let-down after that. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
