<span id="freeTextContainer11498790078933430303">The world kinda ends with an event called Calamity. Ordinary people get superpowers? Kinda sounds cool huh? <br/>Well they don&apos;t use their powers for good. They use those suckers to rule the world!<br/><a href='http://imgur.com/CUhKOr4' rel='nofollow noopener'>
