  <span id="freeText11498790078933430303" style="display:none">The world kinda ends with an event called Calamity. Ordinary people get superpowers? Kinda sounds cool huh? <br>Well they don't use their powers for good. They use those suckers to rule the world!<br><a href="http://imgur.com/CUhKOr4" rel="nofollow noopener">
